  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe currently do not have the ability to send a `value` with our transactions. This was due to a custom encoding format which we implemented which didn't have a `value` field -- that's dumb! Additionally, supporting a custom tx format is annoying for staying 1:1 with eth1.x, especially with the introduction of transaction envelopes. \r\n\r\nOnce we've added support for RLP transactions we will be in a much better place with our transaction ingestion logic.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n_Pretty much blocked by_ https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/issues/495\r\n\r\nTODO\r\n\r\n- [x] Update `SequencerEntrypoint` to decode RLP transactions instead of custom encoding.\r\n- [x] Update batch submitter to operate on raw transactions\r\n- [x] Change `core-utils` (maybe `data-transport-layer` as well) to use the new RLP encoding format\r\n- [x] Update `l2geth` to encode using RLP, not our custom format.\r\n\r\n# In Depth\r\n## Contracts\r\nImplementation: https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/contracts/pull/300/files\r\n\r\nFinish and merge this PR.\r\n\r\n## Batch Submitter\r\nImplementation: https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/batch-submitter/pull/56\r\n\r\nFinish and merge this PR.\r\n\r\n## core-utils\r\nUpdate the encoding which we use here: https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/master/packages/core-utils/src/coders/ecdsa-coder.ts#L54\r\n\r\nRename this encoding to `EIP155Transaction` because right now it's a weird name \"ECDSA transaction\" which is not descriptive.\r\n\r\n## data transport layer\r\nRe-integrate: https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/data-transport-layer/pull/72\r\n\r\nAll contain references to old types. We've got to update these.\r\n\r\n## l2geth\r\nRemove:\r\n- https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/41cfbd166e9a1c52a9caf7782662bcda2cc2dd9f/l2geth/internal/ethapi/api.go#L1747\r\n\r\nUpdate:\r\n- https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/41cfbd166e9a1c52a9caf7782662bcda2cc2dd9f/l2geth/rollup/sync_service.go#L711\r\n- https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/7e9ca1eb2d1e1665539eaeadfb573a768bb6f601/l2geth/rollup/client.go#L105",
